trans-unit.source: Represents a dictionary of <xref href="System.Windows.Media.CharacterMetrics"></xref> objects for a device font that is indexed by Unicode scalar values.
Adds a character code and associated <xref href="System.Windows.Media.CharacterMetrics"></xref> value to the collection using a key/value pair.
The key/value pair representing the character code and associated <xref href="System.Windows.Media.CharacterMetrics"></xref> value.

A value of type <xref href="System.Int32"></xref> representing the character code.

Removes all elements from the collection.

`true` if the dictionary contains the represented by the character code in item; otherwise, `false`.
Determines whether the collection contains the specified character code.
A value of type <xref href="System.Int32"></xref> representing the character code.
`true` if the dictionary contains key; otherwise, `false`.

The zero-based index in array at which copying begins.
Gets the number of elements in the collection.

The key/value pair representing the character code and associated <xref href="System.Windows.Media.CharacterMetrics"></xref> value.

If the return value is `false`, `value` is set to `null`.
